---
---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-soft via-white to-white py-20 md:py-32">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-pink-light opacity-30 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 -left-16 w-72 h-72 rounded-full bg-purple-accent opacity-10 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
    <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
      <span class="inline-block bg-pink-soft text-pink-primary text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6">
        💅 Manicure a domicilio — Santiago
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-6">
        Tu manicure a domicilio,<br>
        <span class="text-pink-primary">cuando quieras</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-500 mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto md:mx-0">
        Escoge tu manicurista, elige el servicio y agenda en segundos. Sin salir de casa.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
        <a
          href="#manicuristas"
          class="inline-block bg-pink-primary text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg hover:bg-opacity-90 transition shadow-lg shadow-pink-light"
        >
          Reservar ahora
        </a>
        <a
          href="#como-funciona"
          class="inline-block border-2 border-pink-light text-pink-primary font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg hover:bg-pink-soft transition"
        >
          Cómo funciona
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-400">⭐️ +200 clientes satisfechas en Santiago</p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1 flex justify-center">
      <div class="relative w-72 h-72 md:w-96 md:h-96">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-light to-purple-accent opacity-20"></div>
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604654894610-df63bc536371?w=600&q=80"
          alt="Manicure profesional a domicilio"
          class="relative z-10 w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-2xl"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
